{
  "stem": "4361.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know how to cry, I think, how to mourn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was one way, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was so much pain, so much bitterness, and so much anger and encountering this?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that-- that's why I said that it was the height of my idealism and the end of it, because I came home to this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, one nice day-- May-- I went-- the washerwoman that we had who was awfully decent, she brought to me one morning some-- my mother's fur coat and some items that apparently, my mother gave her to keep.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was very decent, and she kept it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she brought it back to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she also brought a big basket of cherries from her own orchard or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went with that basket of cherries to this friend's little drugstore [NON-ENGLISH] gathering hole because I knew that I'd find some-- some survivors there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had nobody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we were young kids, not yet 20, and-- and-- and what do you do?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I walked in and I had this basket in my hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, come on, guys, girls, here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they each took cherries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, I heard the voice in Romanian-- because we were talking Hungarian-- in Romanian, well, miss, don't I get any cherries?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I look and the voice comes from the back of the store and comes forth a very, very handsome Russian officer, very handsome.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But more than his handsomeness, what I remembered was the smiling eyes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, sure, and he had some cherries.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
